from dogpile.cache import make_region
my_regions = {'short': make_region().configure('dogpile.cache.memory',
    expiration_time=1), 'long': make_region().configure(
    'dogpile.cache.memory', expiration_time=60), 'myregion': make_region().
    configure('dogpile.cache.memory', expiration_time=60)}
return my_regions
